'''Mukul S. Anand''' ([[11 October]], [[1951]] - [[7 September]] [[1997]]) was an [[Indian film]] producer and director.

His most notable films included ''[[Sultanat]]'' (1986), ''[[Agneepath]]'' (1990 ''[[Hum (film)|Hum]]'' (1991) and ''[[Khuda Gawah]]'' (1992).

He died in [[1997]] while filming the movie ''[[Dus (1997 film)|Dus]]'' which was left incomplete after his death and never released. Promo videos and clips from what was shot of the film can be seen on his official website.

